{"tid":1181583,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"新手想添置鋼琴","createTime":"2019-06-01T17:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T15:00:39.000Z","uid":154783,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da2f7cff9673b525419cad72522ce876e708779d","tid":1181583,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:25:19.000Z","msg":"小妹跟老師學咗一個月琴<br />\n發現彈琴嘅樂趣真係無與倫比<br />\n但每次都要去琴房租好辛苦<br />\n長期book唔到 啲琴又舊 最戇鳩係走走地音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去琴行睇過發現部部都幾萬起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去琴行試咗唔同價位嘅琴同電子琴<br />\n實在唔喜歡電子琴個手感 所以應該唔會考慮<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位覺得要預幾錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有無巴絲想放二手琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（唔想收推銷所以唔留tg了，你留tg我會搵返你）<br />\n<br />\n感激不盡"},{"pid":"50ae843948e3753142c9fdd3faabed3bec1731a9","tid":1181583,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"放心啦我一定會好錫部琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045d1e07334861ce8190ff8b7d85d7174326cb71","tid":1181583,"uid":3694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50ae843948e3753142c9fdd3faabed3bec1731a9","tid":1181583,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"放心啦我一定會好錫部琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:41:15.000Z","msg":"有心學咪分期供部琴囉，Yamaha直身琴都係幾雞嘢咋嘛..."},{"pid":"c7b1f1b86e33156eb80fffa036f28b4b7e9f6ae5","tid":1181583,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"045d1e07334861ce8190ff8b7d85d7174326cb71","tid":1181583,"uid":3694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50ae843948e3753142c9fdd3faabed3bec1731a9","tid":1181583,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"放心啦我一定會好錫部琴<img src=\"/as